<item>
            <title>[LU-1679] On a machine with no zfs installed master fails to build</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1679</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It would appear that master does not build the spl/zfs modules but does then try to build a spl/zfs enabled lustre.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct behavior should be that lustre can be successfully built without zfs/spl, i.e. if a user does not want zfs/spl they should not be required to build it.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A build console is attached.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
